trans-unit.source: Provides an interface that can extend a designer host to support loading from a serialized state.
trans-unit.target: Gir et grensesnitt som kan utvide designer vert for å støtte lasting fra en serialisert tilstand.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost> can implement this interface to enable support for loading by a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost>kan implementerer dette grensesnittet for å aktivere støtte for innlasting av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost>

trans-unit.source: The designer loader informs the designer host that it needs to invoke a load or reload so that the designer host can perform additional tasks at these times.
trans-unit.target: Designer-laster informerer designer verten, må aktivere en belastning eller Last inn på nytt slik at designer verten kan utføre flere aktiviteter på disse tidspunkter.

trans-unit.source: This class is isolated from <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost> to emphasize that the designer loader, not the designer host, must initiate all loading and reloading of the design document.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er isolert fra <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost>til å fremheve at designer-laster, ikke designer verten, må starte alle lasting og omstart av design-dokument.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader> that loads the design document calls this method to indicate that the load terminated.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader>som laster design-dokument kaller opp denne metoden for å indikere at belastningen ble avsluttet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader>

trans-unit.source: If errors are encountered during loading, they must be passed in the `errorCollection` parameter as a collection of exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det oppstår feil under innlasting av, må de sendes på den `errorCollection` parameteren som en samling med unntak.

trans-unit.source: If they are not exceptions, the designer loader host can call <xref:System.Object.ToString%2A> on them and pass them as a collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis de ikke er unntak, designer laster verten kan ringe <xref:System.Object.ToString%2A>på dem og sende dem som en samling.</xref:System.Object.ToString%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the load is successful, then the `errorCollection` parameter must be either `null` or an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den er fullført, og deretter den `errorCollection` -parameteren må være enten `null` eller en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: The fully qualified name of the base class of the document that this designer is designing.
trans-unit.target: Fullstendige navnet på basisklassen i dokumentet utformeren utformer.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the designer is successfully loaded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis designer er lastet inn; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A collection containing the errors encountered during load, if any.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder feilene som oppstod under innlasting, hvis noen.

trans-unit.source: If no errors were encountered, pass either an empty collection or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen feil ble funnet, sendes en tom samling eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader> calls this method to reload the design document.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader>kaller opp denne metoden for å laste inn design-dokument.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.DesignerLoader>
